Why HIStory is the best match:
- HIStory is described as a double‑disc pop/dance set with glossy, vocal‑forward production, hook‑heavy, danceable singles, remixes and club‑ready arrangements. Those features directly map to my primary preferences: tight, rhythm‑forward dance production, punchy low end, layered synths/strings and strong vocal hooks designed for immediate impact and replay value.
